    <h1>Bring me the question your team keeps circling around.</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">I speak and facilitate around software architecture, AI-assisted development, DevOps, Zen, and human-centered technical leadership. We start with what feels alive, stuck, or unclear, then shape the right talk, workshop, or conversation around it.</p>
